## graphify

Knowledge graph at `graphify-out/`. Post-commit hook keeps `graph.json` current.

- Codebase questions: `graphify query "<question>"` before wide grep when `graphify-out/graph.json` exists.
- Relationships: `graphify path "<A>" "<B>"`. Concepts: `graphify explain "<concept>"`.
